1576475719--SELECT online.assist_prd,online.cus_no,b.cus_name,
		case when online.prd_sku_id != '' then b.qty else ifnull(a.qty,0) end  as qty,
		case when online.prd_sku_id != '' then (case when z.prd_sku_id = online.prd_sku_id then '已绑定' else '未绑定' end) else (case when product.prd_id = online.prd_id then '已绑定' else '未绑定' end) end  as binding,
		online.id AS on_id,online.outer_iid AS outer_iid,online.shopid AS on_shopid,online.title AS on_title,online.pic AS on_pic,online.outer_iid AS on_outer_id,online.have_sku,online.num_iid as on_num_iid,
				product.id AS sys_id,product.prd_no AS sys_prd_no,product.title AS sys_title,product.pic_path AS sys_pic,online.prd_id,online.replace_prd_no,
				online.cid_name,online.goods_no,online.brand,online.material,online.material_in,online.standard,online.security,online.retailPrice,online.addtime,online.num_iid,online.cost_price,online.stalls_no  
				FROM u15998235709_product_online AS online 
				LEFT JOIN u15998235709_product AS product ON product.prd_id = online.prd_id 
				LEFT JOIN (select prd_id,sum(qty) as qty from u15998235709_prdt_wms_qty group by prd_id) as a on a.prd_id = online.prd_id
				LEFT JOIN (select prd_sku_id,sum(qty) as qty from u15998235709_prdt_wms_qty where prd_sku_id<>'' group by prd_sku_id) as b on b.prd_sku_id = online.prd_sku_id
				LEFT JOIN u15998235709_cust b on online.cus_no=b.cus_no 
				LEFT JOIN(select prd_id,prd_sku_id from u15998235709_product_sku) z on z.prd_sku_id = online.prd_sku_id
				
				WHERE 1 AND online.shopid = 'IKUCUN-沐诗妤' 
				ORDER BY online.id  ASC limit 0,20

1576475780--SELECT a.system_id,c.system_name,COUNT(1) AS counts, b.nums, SUM(deposit_money) AS total_deposit, SUM(express_money) AS total_express, SUM(take_price) AS take_money, SUM(other_money) AS other_money, SUM(prd_money) AS prd_express, a.ADDDATE, d.balance FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log AS a 
				INNER JOIN (
					SELECT system_id,ADDDATE,balance FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log m
					INNER JOIN (
						SELECT MAX(id) AS id FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log where system_id = '' and addtime > '' and addtime < '1579154180'  GROUP BY ADDDATE 
					) n ON n.id = m.id
				) d ON a.ADDDATE = d.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN (SELECT system_id,COUNT(1) AS nums,ADDDATE FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log WHERE tid LIKE 'CZ%' GROUP BY system_id,ADDDATE) b
				ON a.system_id = b.system_id and a.ADDDATE = b.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN u15998235709_drop_shipping_client c ON a.system_id = c.system_id
				 where 1=1
				GROUP BY a.system_id,a.adddate ORDER BY a.ADDTIME DESC limit 0,50
1576475780--SELECT a.system_id,c.system_name,COUNT(1) AS counts, b.nums, SUM(deposit_money) AS total_deposit, SUM(express_money) AS total_express, SUM(take_price) AS take_money, SUM(other_money) AS other_money, SUM(prd_money) AS prd_express, a.ADDDATE, d.balance FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log AS a 
				INNER JOIN (
					SELECT system_id,ADDDATE,balance FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log m
					INNER JOIN (
						SELECT MAX(id) AS id FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log where system_id = '' and addtime > '' and addtime < '1579154180'  GROUP BY ADDDATE 
					) n ON n.id = m.id
				) d ON a.ADDDATE = d.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN (SELECT system_id,COUNT(1) AS nums,ADDDATE FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log WHERE tid LIKE 'CZ%' GROUP BY system_id,ADDDATE) b
				ON a.system_id = b.system_id and a.ADDDATE = b.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN u15998235709_drop_shipping_client c ON a.system_id = c.system_id
				 where 1=1
				GROUP BY a.system_id,a.adddate ORDER BY a.ADDTIME DESC

				INNER JOIN (
					SELECT system_id,ADDDATE,balance FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log m
					INNER JOIN (
						SELECT MAX(id) AS id FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log where system_id = '' and addtime > '' and addtime < '1579154477'  GROUP BY ADDDATE 
					) n ON n.id = m.id
				) d ON a.ADDDATE = d.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN (SELECT system_id,COUNT(1) AS nums,ADDDATE FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log WHERE tid LIKE 'CZ%' GROUP BY system_id,ADDDATE) b
				ON a.system_id = b.system_id and a.ADDDATE = b.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN u15998235709_drop_shipping_client c ON a.system_id = c.system_id

				GROUP BY a.system_id,a.adddate ORDER BY a.ADDTIME DESC limit 0,50

1576476461--SELECT a.system_id,c.system_name,COUNT(1) AS counts, b.nums, SUM(deposit_money) AS total_deposit, SUM(express_money) AS total_express, SUM(take_price) AS take_money, SUM(other_money) AS other_money, SUM(prd_money) AS prd_express, a.ADDDATE, d.balance FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log AS a 
				INNER JOIN (
					SELECT system_id,ADDDATE,balance FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log m
					INNER JOIN (
						SELECT MAX(id) AS id FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log where system_id = '' and addtime > '' and addtime < '1579154861'  GROUP BY ADDDATE 
					) n ON n.id = m.id
				) d ON a.ADDDATE = d.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN (SELECT system_id,COUNT(1) AS nums,ADDDATE FROM u15998235709_drop_shipping_pay_log WHERE tid LIKE 'CZ%' GROUP BY system_id,ADDDATE) b
				ON a.system_id = b.system_id and a.ADDDATE = b.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN u15998235709_drop_shipping_client c ON a.system_id = c.system_id
				 where 1=1
				GROUP BY a.system_id,a.adddate ORDER BY a.ADDTIME DESC limit 0,50
